{"name": "MHR Burger's", "phone": "018-287 7885", "lat": 2.4778713999999997, "lng": 101.85191739999999, "review": [{"r_name": "Muzamli Mihat", "id": "", "r_item": "-", "r_review": "This place is great! We can choose to dine in outside while listening to the busking band or dine inside the air-conditioning area in peace. The atmosphere is chill and cool but the staff is also really friendly. The food is absolutely amazing, and for their prices it's truly 100% worth it to spend.", "r_ts": ""}, {"r_name": "Joy Joy", "id": "", "r_item": "-", "r_review": "Food portion is worth the price. Fried rice has some fragrance and vege to complement the looks. Paired with crispy fried chicken that’s juicy and thick. There’s a side salad (some onion and tomato slices) with slightly spicy dressing. Drinks was quite large. Ordered the lychee jasmine mojito but didn’t taste jasmine nor see lychee fruit only overpowered by the strong lychee syrup and mint leaves. Peach mojito was also just peach syrup with a wedge of lemon and some leaves. It’s a QR order system and pay once order. It was quite warm in the shop only with fans on. When request to on one of the aircond, it was informed that the aircond has spoilt.", "r_ts": ""}, {"r_name": "Andre Lucas", "id": "", "r_item": "-", "r_review": "One of the best burger restaurant I’ve been in PD. Everything extra cheese. Price also reasonable. Great service too.", "r_ts": ""}, {"r_name": "Ahmad Nizam", "id": "", "r_item": "-", "r_review": "The just ok. But the staff service ia excellent. Recommend to eat inside aircond area because outside is hot because near with sea. Reccomend to try their grill chicken roti john. Nearby parking always full and need to park far away from restaurant. Need to pay first before food arrive. Besides cash thia restaurant accept credit card and online payment.", "r_ts": ""}, {"r_name": "Great Unique Group Venture", "id": "", "r_item": "-", "r_review": "I believe this MHR burgers should enhance the taste of their food and drinks as the top priority, along with the ingredients used in their dishes. Currently, the food and drinks here are somewhat underwhelming, almost as if they are producing them half-heartedly. In the food and beverage industry, the most crucial aspect is to prioritize customer satisfaction before considering the financial aspects (prices). Think about it this way, if the food and drinks are very tasty, customers will undoubtedly praise them and recommend them to their friends. They will also come back for repeat visits. But if it's the other way around, you surely understand the implications. I apologize, but deep down in my heart, I want our Malay business to always maintain standards in order to be a successful business.", "r_ts": ""}, {"r_name": "Sera Woon", "id": "", "r_item": "-", "r_review": "Reasonable price, best to take a family set because it comes with free drink in a jug 🙂 so far it's good. Just need to improve on the app used for ordering and payment - quite laggy.
